25 ARTICLE X
26 POWERS AND DUTIES OF THE INTERSTATE COMMISSION
27 The Interstate Commission shall have the following powers:
28 A. To provide for dispute resolution among member states.
29 B. To promulgate rules and take all necessary actions to
CRM H03106'25 (H-2) hsb4ze

